I kinda wonder though how the 20% magic resist for 1 minute would compare with the full heal from IP in a typical fight.  If ya pop it at the start of a fight before CC is cast that's 20% less duration on that (stacked with base resists, resist buffs and Determination ... hah hah hah).  Hmmm, our server is mostly Albs/Hibs, so I guess in that sort of environment it would help more than if Mid was dominant and you were dealing with more melee.  I'll have to ponder that one though. <p>Nirala Kindred<br>
